data.description: Come see this Fabulous 4 sided Brick home in established Westbridge community. Two story entry, formal living and dining rooms, updated eat in kitchen. This one has hardwoods in foyer and family room and upgraded tile flooring in all bathrooms. The hidden wet bar in the family room will be a hit for entertaining. Upgraded flooring in the gorgeous glass enclosed sunroom off the family room overlooks the half acre+ backyard. Upstairs an oversized Owner's suite with updated bath and huge additional bedrooms. The guest room has been updated. Upgraded flooring installed in all rooms. New carpeting in office and dining room. Don't miss the bonus room above the side entry Garage! Fresh coat of paint throughout the entire house!
